Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你需要什么  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever you need, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你需要什么  我都会告诉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll tell them whatever you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让他们这么对你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not gonna let them do this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, my God, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得这次会不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What makes you think it'll be different this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得你能把他抓起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What makes you think you can put him away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来操心安德鲁·厄拉姆的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You need to let me worry about Andrew Earlham.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-等你...  -等我们提出指控就给你电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Will you call me as soon as you - As soon as we press charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs16\i1}三个月后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-旅途怎么样  -很不错  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How was the journey down? - Good. Really easy. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你应该让我来找你的  -不不不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You really should have let me come to you. - Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很不错  我一直很想来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is nice. I always wanted to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说你平时看上去不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not that you don't always look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OK. Er, drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想喝点什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿吧  如果你不介意的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Actually, I'll get them, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  让我去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please. Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  跑跑跑跑跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go on. Run, run, run, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  你们别动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, you're staying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们来了  玩得开心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, there's my boys. Did you have a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们玩得开心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  我烧好茶了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go on, I've got tea ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll be with you in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一直问我会不会留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So they kept asking if I was going to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it's er...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能需要点时间习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's gonna take some time for them to get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们会习惯的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没必要习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的错  凯蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You did this, Katy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不关别人的事  -我只想求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No-one else. - All I'm asking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为了他们试试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is that we try, for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让他们在成长的过程中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want them growing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我们两边拖拽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}up being pulled in two different directions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-夹在中间  -我也不想那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- caught in the middle - And I don't want that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的所作所为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But what you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法忘记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没法原谅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or forgive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Daddy's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周二见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See you on Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在地铁上  给一位女士让了座\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I was on the Tube and I offered my seat to this, erm, lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她问  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she said, 'Why?'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  因为你怀孕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I said, 'Well, because you're pregnant.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她说  我没有怀孕  -天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- And she said, 'l'm not pregnant.' - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你说了什么  -我想不到该说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What did you say? - I couldn't think of anything to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看上去就像怀孕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, she looked pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子的形状\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From the shape of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来很确定...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}l was really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她只会觉得你很绅士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe she just thought you were being chivalrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让座给一个胖子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By offering my seat to a fat person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在我只要在车上看到有人站着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So now whenever I'm on a train and I see someone standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我脑中就会浮现出无数想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}l have a million thoughts going through my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们真的是怀孕了吗  他们是不是没那么老\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are they not actually pregnant? Are they not that old?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们是不是女的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are they not even a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是个雷区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a minefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太不公平了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not fair, though, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想做点好事  然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were just trying to do something nice and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  那是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is it? Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳拉  是他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Laura, is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被二次调查了  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was investigated a second time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:10:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察把他的生活翻了个底朝天  什么都没发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Police turned his life upside down and found precisely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就把他放了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They just let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算哈蒙警长指控了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even after DI Harmon's charges,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也找不到抓他的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they couldn't find anything to put him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是因为他知道怎么销毁证据吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He knows how to cover his tracks, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以想象你看到他这样逍遥法外的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't imagine what it must feel like to see him walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愤怒了很久  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I've been angry for long time, but erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会消耗你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it wastes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会把你吞噬掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It eats away at you and erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当我有这种感觉时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Every time I feel that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就像是事情再一次发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's like it's happening all over again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在某一刻  不得不放手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so at some point you have to... let it go or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者至少试一试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}try to, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这杯敬你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here's to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还有多久  -一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- So how much longer? - A month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你找到新地方了吗  -没 很理智吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Have you found a new place yet? - No. Sensible, hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这个鬼地方是当务之急\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}getting the hell out of this place was the priority,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我看的所有房子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but everything I look at,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不太好  要么太小  要么离公路太近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all I see is the bad stuff too small, too close to a road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个房子颜色太黄了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One place was too yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真不能要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a deal breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你让我过了一个愉快的夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks for a lovely night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很高兴跟你见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, it was... it was really good seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  你一路送我回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry. You've come all this way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-而我却不请你进屋  -不不  没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- and I'm not even inviting you in. - No, no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下周见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See you next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Next week it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  伊恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good night, Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  劳拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good night, Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就喝一杯  街角就有家很棒的小酒吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One drink. There's a beautiful little pub just round the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在已经和我约会这么多次了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've been on enough dates with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我这么容易被说服吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think I'm easily persuaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我试了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At least I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但下次吃晚饭  我坚持由我来做饭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But next time, dinner, I'll cook, I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我做瑞士千层酥皮鲑鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If I make my salmon en croute,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我儿子就会走开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}maybe my son will bugger off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们就能单独相处一会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We might have a moment to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那好吧  -太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- All right, then. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OK, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Till next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏洛特  你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Charlotte? Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫劳拉·尼尔森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Laura Nielson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你能来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I appreciate you coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道安德鲁和我说起过你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You should know Andrew told me about you.
