Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是想恐吓我  而且他做到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He just wanted to scare me, and it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我整晚都没睡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't sleep all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为他把我们录下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think he filmed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对我们做的那些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What he did to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他谈到了那晚  谈到了...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He talked about that night. He talked about erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墙上的一幅画\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a picture on my wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我床上很小的细节  那些琐碎的小事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}some tiny detail about my bed, little things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当时在我房间里不可能注意到那些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that he couldn't have noticed in the time he was in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他有时间四周打探  -他说...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He had time to look around. - He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我只要有机会就会重播"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I play that back whenever I get the chance."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是「我会回想」  而是「我会重播」\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not "I think about it", "I play it back."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是一种说法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could just be an expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的那些事  那些细节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The things he said, the detail he went into.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说  他都录下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm telling you, he recorded it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:22:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那个令人作呕的杂种把证据藏在某处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the sick bastard still has it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳拉...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Laura...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那样的男人就是想控制和羞辱女性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Men like him want to control and humiliate women.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么比录下来更羞辱人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's more humiliating than a recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.41,0:22:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了  我们搜过他的家  工作地还有电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop. We searched his house, his work, his computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及他的所有电子设备  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Every electronic device he has, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们什么都没找着  -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- And we found nothing. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他太狡猾了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But he's too smart for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳拉  我需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Laura, what I need you to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不要去做  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is absolutely nothing, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以派一辆巡逻警车守在你家外面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, I can get a patrol car to stay outside your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒  我所有问题都解决了  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great, all my problems are solved
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  你能至少把我说的那些话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, will you pass on what I've said at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转达给你的那个同事吗  只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To your colleagues. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在和他在一起的那个女人  夏洛特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That woman he's with now, Charlotte,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望她平安无事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want her to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我会跟他说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, sure, I'll pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.81,0:23:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你好  警探  -凡妮莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hi, Detective - Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-抱歉打扰了  -没事  只是在赶些文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sorry to bother you. - No bother. I'm catching up on paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚和劳拉·尼尔森通过电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just spoke with Laura Nielson.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳拉  我昨天见到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Laura, yeah, I met her yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.47,0:23:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她认为安德鲁·厄拉姆录下了他的罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She thinks Andrew Earlham records his attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把东西藏在了某个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That he's storing them somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厄拉姆昨晚出现在了她家外面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Earlham turned up outside her house last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他发现了她正在调查他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He found out she's been looking into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你告诉他的  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because you told him? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要让安德鲁坐立不安  愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need Andrew unsettled. Angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样他就会犯错  我们就可以把他绳之以法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's when he'll make mistakes, that's when we'll catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  我们在劳拉住的地方安排了巡逻车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry, we had a squad car on Laura's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不应该让她掺和进来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You shouldn't put her in the middle of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她自己掺和进来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She put herself in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.17,0:23:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是抓住了机会给安德鲁施压\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just took the opportunity to push Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-抱歉  我知道我没发言权  -你当然有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm sorry, I know this isn't my place, but - Course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这项行动多亏了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This operation is down to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望能有更多证据上报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just wish we had more to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:23:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但今晚我要去他家吃完饭  -今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- But tonight I'm going for dinner at his place. - Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美妙周五夜  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great Friday night, huh
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.52,0:24:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住  别让自己有机可乘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remember, don't make yourself too available.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.87,0:24:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过资料了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've read the profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我只是提醒你  因为...  -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm only saying because... - Look, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着批准通过很让人泄气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how frustrating it's been waiting for approval to come through
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们成功在望了  有点信心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we're close now. Just keep the faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.32,0:24:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  警探  -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thanks, Detective. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.56,0:24:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-马上就好  -我们需要你去五号检查室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yep, just a minute. - OK, we need you in Exam 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.87,0:24:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能先从柜子里拿点东西出来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can I grab something from my locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.22,0:25:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了  他们早就在等着了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There isn't much time. They've been waiting already.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.48,0:25:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  咱们去把这个处理完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, then, let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.43,0:25:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴你给我打了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm glad you called.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.36,0:25:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好久都没联系了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.72,0:25:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.86,0:25:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Er, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.60,0:25:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德鲁的手机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andrew's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.61,0:25:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.50,0:25:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为你做任何事  你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd do anything for you, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.97,0:25:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你还在生我的气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even when you're angry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.06,0:25:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你也不会告诉我要这手机干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't suppose you're gonna tell me what that's for?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.41,0:25:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你最好不要知道  -不要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's probably best that you don't know. - Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.96,0:25:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.20,0:26:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你已经释怀了  劳拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought you were moving on with your life, Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.64,0:26:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我必须这么做  -不  你不需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I have to do this. - No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.09,0:26:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从来都不需要做这些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You never had to do any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.08,0:26:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你经历了噩梦般的事  你一直想纠正\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You had a terrible thing happen to you and you tried to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.25,0:26:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是给自己点时间来恢复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Instead of taking time to get better and look after yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.16,0:26:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.91,0:26:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I miss you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.99,0:26:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得你会停止恨我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think you'll ever stop hating me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.71,0:26:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不恨你  凯蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't hate you, Katy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.12,0:26:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...我没法再相信你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just... I can't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.53,0:26:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道要怎么面对你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I don't know how to be around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.57,0:26:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.77,0:26:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when you are ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.40,0:26:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...你知道我在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}..You know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.12,0:27:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-快请进  -你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hi, come in, come in. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.68,0:28:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -就挂这吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thanks. - There you go. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.89,0:28:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wow, you look amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.91,0:28:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-从这里过去就好  -赞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Just through here. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.65,0:28:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-挺香的啊  -谢谢夸奖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That smells good. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.99,0:28:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么特别  就是一些专门订购的食材\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's nothing much, just er, speciality-ordered ingredients
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.46,0:28:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还为此准备了两天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and about 48 hours of preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.83,0:28:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我很高兴你能来  -为何不来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm glad you came. - Why wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.81,0:28:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有人从我柜子里拿走了我的手机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Someone took my phone from a locker today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-真烦人  -没事  我把那个号取消了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That's annoying. - No, it's fine, it's been cancelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.86,0:28:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我订了另一支手机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and there's another one ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.46,0:28:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的  没了手机就好像成了孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know how it is - you lose your phone, you feel like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.76,0:28:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能发短信取消或修改时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How did we ever make social arrangements
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.56,0:28:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们要怎么约人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when we couldn't cancel or change with a text last-minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.50,0:28:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要答应了就会出现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I like to turn up when I've agreed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.97,0:28:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是那么老套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm old-fashioned like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.03,0:28:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me, too.
